# Zod v4

`import { z } from "zod"`. Use `z.object`, `z.coerce.*`, `.min()/.max()/.default()`. Types: `z.infer<typeof schema>`. Refactor legacy Zod patterns to v4 before extending. Colocate with actions as `*.validation.ts`.
